# Lao Li Stocks

Pure frontend scaffold for a stock buy-in / add-on price generator.

## Scripts

- `npm install`
- `npm run dev`
- `npm run build`
- `npm run test`

## Directory structure

- `src/` app source (entry: `src/main.ts`, UI shell: `src/app.ts`)
- `tests/` Vitest tests (unit + UI render)
- `index.html` Vite entry HTML

## Local API key setup

The Alpha Vantage API key is stored only in the browser `localStorage`. Use the UI panel to save, test, or clear it before data refresh is enabled.
